## Invoice Ninja

#### Create Access Token

Go to https://git.web-vision.io/-/profile/personal_access_tokens and Create a token with api scope checked.

```
composer --global config http-basic.git.web-vision.io gitlab-ci-token <your-gitlab-personal-access-token>
```

Now you add this 

```
composer config repositories.34 composer "https://git.web-vision.io/api/v4/group/34/-/packages/composer/packages.json"

```

#### old remove

Add authorization directly to composer repository config:

 https://__token__:<personal_token>@git.web-vision.io/api/v4/group/34/-/packages/composer/packages.json
